text.tspan: How did this guy even get to this mansion? He's from
ancient Egypt. That's a long ways away from Scotland,
where we are right now. He has completely renovated
the room that he lives in: it's sandy, it's walls are made
of stone, and it overall looks like ancient Egypt. It's
even windy in there! How crazy is that? I imagine it's
to remind him of home. How sweet.
